Corporate Events

Looking to add a touch of enchantment and wonder to your corporate event? Illuminadi specializes in creating magical experiences that leave a lasting impact.

Elevate your corporate event with astonishing magic

Illuminadi’s captivating performances, tailored for corporate gatherings, conferences, and galas, will dazzle your guests and ignite their imagination. Whether you need captivating entertainment during cocktail hours, a mind-bending stage show, or intimate close-up magic at your booth, Illuminadi delivers an unforgettable experience that will make your corporate event truly memorable.

Socially Distant

Parlour magic is compliant with CDC recommendations. Since the illusions are larger and more visually striking than close up magic, the audience can enjoy the magic from afar without feeling isolated.

Interactive

You don’t have to sit next to the magician to feel like a part of the show! The audience is involved and invested in the magic in their own seats, even when they’re spaced 6 feet apart!

Monthly

Illuminadi shows are as varied as the Nashville weather. Every month brings with it a fresh new show. Restore your wonder monthly with a different mind bending show.

See the Magic

Discover the magic of Illuminadi’s recent shows—see the excitement, joy, and connection he brings to professional events.

Play Video

Different types of shows to choose from:

Close-Up

The intimate art of producing astonishing illusions within close proximity to the audience.

Parlor

The extravagant art of creating larger than life illusions that can amaze from afar.

Mentalism

The cerebral art of utilizing human psychology and body language to provide unexplainable magical experiences
